<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>G11. Possessive Forms</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,500;1,500&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;700&family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #f5f0e8;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --green-dark: #4a6741;
    --green-mid: #5a7a50;
    --green-light: #e8f0e5;
    --green-card: #3d5c35;
    --gold: #c8972a;
    --gold-light: #fdf3e0;
    --cream: #faf7f0;
    --brown: #6b5c3e;
    --brown-light: #f0e8d8;
    --text: #2d2d2d;
    --muted: #7a7a7a;
    --border: #ddd6c8;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; line-height: 1.7; padding-bottom: 80px; }

  /* HEADER */
  .lesson-header { background: #0a1628; padding: 36px 24px 32px; text-align: center; }
  .gbc-badge { display: inline-block; border: 1px solid rgba(0,242,255,0.5); color: rgba(0,242,255,0.8); font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .lesson-num-title { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .lesson-main-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 44px; font-weight: 500; color: #00f2ff; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .lesson-sub { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }

  /* TOC */
  .toc { background: var(--green-dark); padding: 12px 20px; display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
  .toc a { font-size: 12px; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); text-decoration: none; }
  .toc a:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: #fff; }

  /* LAYOUT */
  .content { max-width: 740px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

  /* SECTION */
  .section { margin-top: 28px; background: var(--white); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .section-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding: 14px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .section-num { width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; color: #fff; }
  .section-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
  .section-en { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-left: 6px; }
  .section-body { padding: 20px; }

  /* KEY CARD */
  .key-card { background: var(--green-card); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .key-label { font-size: 11px; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .key-text { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 500; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .key-kr { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }

  /* CONCEPT BOX */
  .concept-box { background: var(--green-light); border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; border-left: 4px solid var(--green-mid); }
  .concept-box p { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .concept-box p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* RULE GRID */
  .rule-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .rule-card { padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .rule-label { font-size: 10px; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .rule-example { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; }
  .rule-example strong { font-weight: 700; }
  .r-is { background: var(--green-light); border-color: #b8d4b0; }
  .r-is .rule-label { color: var(--green-dark); }
  .r-is .rule-example strong { color: var(--green-dark); }
  .r-are { background: #e8f4e8; border-color: #a8ccaa; }
  .r-are .rule-label { color: #3a6640; }
  .r-are .rule-example strong { color: #3a6640; }
  .r-neg { background: #fdf0e0; border-color: #e8c88a; }
  .r-neg .rule-label { color: #8a5a1a; }
  .r-neg .rule-example strong { color: #8a5a1a; }
  .r-q { background: var(--brown-light); border-color: #d4c0a0; }
  .r-q .rule-label { color: var(--brown); }
  .r-q .rule-example strong { color: var(--brown); }

  /* BULLET LIST */
  .rule-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .rule-list li { font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 12px; background: var(--cream); border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid var(--green-mid); }
  .rule-list li strong { color: var(--green-dark); font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }

  /* EXAMPLE LIST */
  .ex-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .ex-list li { padding: 12px 16px; background: var(--cream); border-radius: 10px; border-left: 4px solid var(--green-mid); font-size: 14px; }
  .ex-list li .en { color: var(--green-dark); font-weight: 700; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }
  .ex-list li .kr { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; display: block; margin-top: 2px; }
  .ex-q { border-left-color: var(--brown) !important; }
  .ex-q .en { color: var(--brown) !important; }

  /* DIALOGUE */
  .dialogue { background: var(--cream); border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .d-title { font-size: 10px; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .d-line { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .d-line .sp { color: var(--green-dark); font-weight: 700; margin-right: 6px; }
  .d-line .key { color: var(--green-dark); font-weight: 700; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }

  /* PRACTICE */
  .practice-item { padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 14px; background: var(--cream); }
  .practice-item .original { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 13px; }
  .practice-item .result { color: var(--green-dark); font-weight: 700; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }

  /* PATTERN BOX */
  .pattern-box { background: var(--gold-light); border: 1px solid #e8c88a; border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .pattern-box .p-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--gold); font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .pattern-box .p-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--brown); }
  .pattern-box .p-text strong { color: #7a5010; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }

  /* MISTAKE BOX */
  .mistake-box { background: #fff5f5; border: 1px solid #f4c0c0; border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .mistake-box .wrong { color: #c0392b; font-size: 13px; text-decoration: line-through; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .mistake-box .right { color: var(--green-dark); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }
  .mistake-box .reason { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; margin-top: 4px; }

  /* TIP BOX */
  .tip-box { background: #e8f0ff; border: 1px solid #b8c8f0; border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px 16px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .tip-box .tip-label { font-size: 11px; color: #3050a0; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .tip-box .tip-text { font-size: 14px; color: #1a2a60; }

  /* CHECKLIST */
  .checklist { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .checklist li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; font-size: 14px; padding: 10px 14px; background: var(--cream); border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer; }
  .chk { width: 20px; height: 20px; border: 2px solid var(--green-mid); border-radius: 6px; flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: all 0.2s; background: #fff; }
  .chk.on { background: var(--green-mid); border-color: var(--green-dark); }
  .chk.on::after { content: '\2713'; color: #fff; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer-nav { background: var(--green-dark); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 14px 24px; margin-top: 32px; }
  .fnav-btn { padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; border: none; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }
  .fnav-prev { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color: #fff; }
  .fnav-center { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }
  .fnav-next { background: var(--gold); color: #000; }
</style>
</head>
<body data-grammar-id="G11">

<div class="lesson-header">
  <div class="gbc-badge">CEC GRAMMAR BASECAMP</div>
  <div class="lesson-num-title">G11 · Basic Grammar</div>
  <div class="lesson-main-title">Possessive Forms</div>
  <div class="lesson-sub">소유격 — my, your, his, her, our, their</div>
</div>

<div class="toc">
  <a href="#concept">기본 개념</a>
  <a href="#grammar">문법 규칙</a>
  <a href="#positive">긍정문</a>
  <a href="#question">의문문</a>
  <a href="#dialogue">대화 흐름</a>
  <a href="#combining">문장 결합</a>
  <a href="#reallife">실생활</a>
  <a href="#patterns">패턴</a>
  <a href="#mistakes">흔한 실수</a>
  <a href="#tips">레벨업 팁</a>
  <a href="#practice">연습문제</a>
  <a href="#check">자가진단</a>
</div>

<div class="content">

  <!-- 1. 기본 개념 -->
  <div class="section" id="s1">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num" style="background:var(--green-dark);">1</div>
      <div><span class="section-title">기본 개념</span><span class="section-en">BASIC CONCEPT</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="key-card">
        <div class="key-label">⭐ TODAY'S KEY GRAMMAR</div>
        <div class="key-text">Possessive Forms</div>
        <div class="key-kr">소유격 — my, your, his, her, our, their</div>
      </div>
      <div class="concept-box">
        <p><strong style="color:var(--green-dark)">소유 형용사 (Possessive Adjective)</strong> → 사람이나 사물의 <strong>소유</strong>를 나타냅니다.</p>
        <p><strong style="color:#3a6640">주요 형태</strong> → <strong>my</strong>, <strong>your</strong>, <strong>his</strong>, <strong>her</strong> + 명사</p>
        <p>항상 명사 <strong>앞</strong>에 위치하여, '누구의 것'인지 알려주는 역할을 합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="ex-list">
        <li>This is <span class="en">my</span> book.<span class="kr">이것은 나의 책이다.</span></li>
        <li>That is <span class="en">her</span> bag.<span class="kr">저것은 그녀의 가방이다.</span></li>
        <li>Is this <span class="en">his</span> phone?<span class="kr">이것은 그의 전화기니?</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 2. 문법 규칙 -->
  <div class="section" id="s2">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num" style="background:#3a6640;">2</div>
      <div><span class="section-title">문법 규칙</span><span class="section-en">GRAMMAR RULES</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="rule-grid">
        <div class="rule-card r-is">
          <div class="rule-label">1인칭 · FIRST PERSON</div>
          <div class="rule-example"><strong>I → my</strong><br><span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)">my book</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="rule-card r-are">
          <div class="rule-label">2인칭 · SECOND PERSON</div>
          <div class="rule-example"><strong>you → your</strong><br><span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)">your pen</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="rule-card r-neg">
          <div class="rule-label">3인칭 남성 · THIRD (MALE)</div>
          <div class="rule-example"><strong>he → his</strong><br><span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)">his phone</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="rule-card r-q">
          <div class="rule-label">3인칭 여성 · THIRD (FEMALE)</div>
          <div class="rule-example"><strong>she → her</strong><br><span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)">her bag</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul class="rule-list">
        <li><strong>위치:</strong> 소유 형용사는 명사 앞에 위치하며, 명사를 수식합니다. (예: your pen)</li>
        <li><strong>수 일치:</strong> 소유 대상 명사가 단수든 복수든 소유 형용사의 형태는 변하지 않습니다.</li>
        <li><strong>예:</strong> my book / my books / her idea / her ideas</li>
        <li><strong>주의:</strong> his는 he에서, her는 she에서 파생됩니다.</li>
        <li><strong>your:</strong> 단수 명사(너의)와 복수 명사(너희들의) 모두에 사용 가능합니다.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 3. 긍정문 예시 -->
  <div class="section" id="s3">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num" style="background:var(--gold); color:#000;">3</div>
      <div><span class="section-title">긍정문 예시</span><span class="section-en">POSITIVE EXAMPLES</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <ul class="ex-list">
        <li>This is <span class="en">my</span> notebook.<span class="kr">이것은 나의 공책이다.</span></li>
        <li>That is <span class="en">your</span> pencil.<span class="kr">저것은 너의 연필이다.</span></li>
        <li>This is <span class="en">his</span> phone.<span class="kr">이것은 그의 전화기이다.</span></li>
        <li>That is <span class="en">her</span> bag.<span class="kr">저것은 그녀의 가방이다.</span></li>
        <li>These are <span class="en">my</span> books.<span class="kr">이것들은 나의 책들이다.</span></li>
        <li>Those are <span class="en">your</span> shoes.<span class="kr">저것들은 너의 신발들이다.</span></li>
        <li>This is <span class="en">his</span> jacket.<span class="kr">이것은 그의 재킷이다.</span></li>
        <li>That is <span class="en">her</span> umbrella.<span class="kr">저것은 그녀의 우산이다.</span></li>
        <li>Is this <span class="en">your</span> key?<span class="kr">이것은 너의 열쇠니?</span></li>
        <li>Yes, it's <span class="en">my</span> key.<span class="kr">응, 나의 열쇠야.</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 4. 의문문 예시 -->
  <div class="section" id="s4">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num" style="background:var(--brown);">4</div>
      <div><span class="section-title">의문문 예시</span><span class="section-en">QUESTION EXAMPLES</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <ul class="ex-list">
        <li class="ex-q"><span class="en">Is</span> this your pen?<span class="kr">이것은 너의 펜이니?</span></li>
        <li class="ex-q"><span class="en">Is</span> that his phone?<span class="kr">저것은 그의 전화기니?</span></li>
        <li class="ex-q"><span class="en">Is</span> this her bag?<span class="kr">이것은 그녀의 가방이니?</span></li>
        <li class="ex-q"><span class="en">Are</span> these your shoes?<span class="kr">이것들은 너의 신발이니?</span></li>
        <li class="ex-q"><span class="en">Are</span> those his books?<span class="kr">저것들은 그의 책들이니?</span></li>
        <li class="ex-q"><span class="en">Is</span> this my notebook?<span class="kr">이것은 나의 공책이니?</span></li>
        <li class="ex-q"><span class="en">Is</span> that her umbrella?<span class="kr">저것은 그녀의 우산이니?</span></li>
        <li class="ex-q"><span class="en">Are</span> these my keys?<span class="kr">이것들은 나의 열쇠니?</span></li>
        <li class="ex-q"><span class="en">Is</span> this your jacket?<span class="kr">이것은 너의 재킷이니?</span></li>
        <li class="ex-q"><span class="en">Are</span> those her glasses?<span class="kr">저것들은 그녀의 안경이니?</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 5. 상황별 대화 흐름 -->
  <div class="section" id="s5">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num" style="background:#5a7a50;">5</div>
      <div><span class="section-title">상황별 대화 흐름</span><span class="section-en">SITUATIONAL DIALOGUES</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="dialogue">
        <div class="d-title">🏫 학교 상황 · SCHOOL</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">A:</span> Is this <span class="key">your</span> notebook?</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">B:</span> No, it's <span class="key">his</span> notebook.</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">A:</span> Okay, I'll give it to him.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="dialogue">
        <div class="d-title">✈️ 여행 상황 · TRAVEL</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">A:</span> Is that <span class="key">her</span> bag?</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">B:</span> Yes, it's <span class="key">her</span> favorite one.</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">A:</span> Let's take it to her.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="dialogue">
        <div class="d-title">💼 직장 상황 · OFFICE</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">A:</span> Are these <span class="key">your</span> files?</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">B:</span> No, they're <span class="key">his</span> files.</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">A:</span> I'll move them to his desk.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="dialogue">
        <div class="d-title">💻 온라인 상황 · ONLINE</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">A:</span> Is this <span class="key">my</span> account?</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">B:</span> Yes, it's <span class="key">your</span> login page.</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">A:</span> Thanks!</div>
      </div>
      <div class="dialogue">
        <div class="d-title">🏠 가족 상황 · FAMILY</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">A:</span> Are those <span class="key">her</span> shoes?</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">B:</span> Yes, they're <span class="key">her</span> new ones.</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">A:</span> She'll be happy.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="dialogue">
        <div class="d-title">🏥 병원 상황 · HOSPITAL</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">A:</span> Is this <span class="key">his</span> medicine?</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">B:</span> Yes, it's <span class="key">his</span> prescription.</div>
        <div class="d-line"><span class="sp">A:</span> I'll give it to him now.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 6. 문장 결합 연습 -->
  <div class="section" id="s6">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num" style="background:var(--green-dark);">6</div>
      <div><span class="section-title">문장 결합 연습</span><span class="section-en">SENTENCE COMBINING</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="practice-item">
        <div class="original">I have a book.</div>
        <div class="result">→ It is my book.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="practice-item">
        <div class="original">You have a pen.</div>
        <div class="result">→ It is your pen.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="practice-item">
        <div class="original">He has a phone.</div>
        <div class="result">→ It is his phone.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="practice-item">
        <div class="original">She has a bag.</div>
        <div class="result">→ It is her bag.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="practice-item">
        <div class="original">I have notebooks.</div>
        <div class="result">→ They are my notebooks.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="practice-item">
        <div class="original">You have shoes.</div>
        <div class="result">→ They are your shoes.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="practice-item">
        <div class="original">He has a jacket.</div>
        <div class="result">→ It is his jacket.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="practice-item">
        <div class="original">She has an umbrella.</div>
        <div class="result">→ It is her umbrella.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="practice-item">
        <div class="original">I have keys.</div>
        <div class="result">→ They are my keys.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="practice-item">
        <div class="original">You have glasses.</div>
        <div class="result">→ They are your glasses.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 7. 실생활 사용 예시 -->
  <div class="section" id="s7">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num" style="background:var(--gold); color:#000;">7</div>
      <div><span class="section-title">실생활 사용 예시</span><span class="section-en">REAL-LIFE USAGE</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <ul class="ex-list">
        <li>This is <span class="en">my</span> notebook. That is <span class="en">her</span> pencil.<span class="kr">🏫 학교 — 나의 공책, 그녀의 연필</span></li>
        <li>These are <span class="en">his</span> files. Is this <span class="en">your</span> report?<span class="kr">💼 직장 — 그의 파일, 당신의 보고서</span></li>
        <li>That is <span class="en">her</span> phone. These are <span class="en">my</span> shoes.<span class="kr">🏠 가족 — 그녀의 전화기, 나의 신발</span></li>
        <li>Is this <span class="en">your</span> account? Yes, it's <span class="en">my</span> login.<span class="kr">💻 온라인 — 당신의 계정, 나의 로그인</span></li>
        <li>This is <span class="en">his</span> medicine. That is <span class="en">her</span> chart.<span class="kr">🏥 병원 — 그의 약, 그녀의 차트</span></li>
        <li>Is that <span class="en">your</span> passport? No, it's <span class="en">his</span>.<span class="kr">✈️ 여행 — 당신의 여권, 그의 것</span></li>
        <li>That is <span class="en">her</span> idea. This is <span class="en">my</span> suggestion.<span class="kr">📋 회의 — 그녀의 아이디어, 나의 제안</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 8. 자주 쓰이는 패턴 -->
  <div class="section" id="s8">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num" style="background:var(--brown);">8</div>
      <div><span class="section-title">자주 쓰이는 패턴</span><span class="section-en">COMMON PATTERNS</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="pattern-box">
        <div class="p-label">소유 형용사 + 단수 명사 · SINGULAR</div>
        <div class="p-text"><strong>my</strong> book, <strong>your</strong> phone, <strong>his</strong> jacket, <strong>her</strong> idea</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pattern-box">
        <div class="p-label">소유 형용사 + 복수 명사 · PLURAL</div>
        <div class="p-text"><strong>my</strong> books, <strong>your</strong> shoes, <strong>his</strong> files, <strong>her</strong> ideas<br><span style="font-size:13px;">소유 형용사 자체는 변하지 않음</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pattern-box">
        <div class="p-label">질문 패턴 · QUESTION</div>
        <div class="p-text"><strong>Is this/that</strong> + 소유 형용사 + 명사?<br><span style="font-size:13px;">Is this your key?</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pattern-box">
        <div class="p-label">대답 패턴 · ANSWER</div>
        <div class="p-text"><strong>Yes, it's my...</strong> / <strong>No, it's his...</strong><br><span style="font-size:13px;">소유 형용사를 사용하여 대답</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pattern-box">
        <div class="p-label">HIS / HER 구분</div>
        <div class="p-text"><strong>His</strong>는 남성(he)의 소유, <strong>Her</strong>는 여성(she)의 소유를 나타냅니다.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 9. 흔한 실수 -->
  <div class="section" id="s9">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num" style="background:#c0392b;">9</div>
      <div><span class="section-title">흔한 실수</span><span class="section-en">COMMON MISTAKES</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="mistake-box">
        <div class="wrong">✗ This is mine book.</div>
        <div class="right">✓ This is my book.</div>
        <div class="reason">mine은 소유대명사, 명사 앞에는 my 사용</div>
      </div>
      <div class="mistake-box">
        <div class="wrong">✗ That is hers bag.</div>
        <div class="right">✓ That is her bag.</div>
        <div class="reason">hers는 소유대명사, 명사 앞에는 her 사용</div>
      </div>
      <div class="mistake-box">
        <div class="wrong">✗ Is this he phone?</div>
        <div class="right">✓ Is this his phone?</div>
        <div class="reason">주격 대명사 he 대신 소유 형용사 his 사용</div>
      </div>
      <div class="mistake-box">
        <div class="wrong">✗ These are me shoes.</div>
        <div class="right">✓ These are my shoes.</div>
        <div class="reason">목적격 대명사 me 대신 소유 형용사 my 사용</div>
      </div>
      <div class="mistake-box">
        <div class="wrong">✗ Those are she glasses.</div>
        <div class="right">✓ Those are her glasses.</div>
        <div class="reason">주격 대명사 she 대신 소유 형용사 her 사용</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 10. 레벨업 팁 -->
  <div class="section" id="s10">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num" style="background:#185fa5;">10</div>
      <div><span class="section-title">레벨업 팁</span><span class="section-en">LEVEL-UP TIPS</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="tip-box">
        <div class="tip-label">TIP 1 · 소유 대명사 비교</div>
        <div class="tip-text">my (소유 형용사) vs. mine (소유 대명사). my는 명사 앞에, mine은 단독으로 문장 끝에 사용됩니다. (예: This is my pen. / This pen is mine.)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-box">
        <div class="tip-label">TIP 2 · IT'S VS. ITS</div>
        <div class="tip-text">'It's'는 it is의 축약형이고, 'Its'는 사물(it)의 소유 형용사입니다. (예: The dog chased its tail.)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-box">
        <div class="tip-label">TIP 3 · 이름의 소유</div>
        <div class="tip-text">사람 이름은 's를 붙여 소유를 나타낼 수 있습니다. (예: This is Jane's book. = This is her book.)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-box">
        <div class="tip-label">TIP 4 · 반복 연습</div>
        <div class="tip-text">"Is this your X?"라고 묻고, "Yes, it's my X." 또는 "No, it's his/her X."라고 답하는 연습을 통해 문장 구조를 자동화하세요.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 11. 연습문제 -->
  <div class="section" id="s11">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num" style="background:var(--green-dark);">11</div>
      <div><span class="section-title">연습문제</span><span class="section-en">PRACTICE EXERCISES</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <p style="font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:14px;">빈칸에 알맞은 소유 형용사(my, your, his, her)를 넣으세요.</p>
      <ul class="rule-list">
        <li>I have a dog. It is ___ dog. <strong style="color:var(--green-dark)">(my)</strong></li>
        <li>You have a pen. It is ___ pen. <strong style="color:var(--green-dark)">(your)</strong></li>
        <li>He has a jacket. This is ___ jacket. <strong style="color:var(--green-dark)">(his)</strong></li>
        <li>She has a bag. That is ___ bag. <strong style="color:var(--green-dark)">(her)</strong></li>
        <li>I have a book. → It is ___ book. <strong style="color:var(--green-dark)">(my)</strong></li>
        <li>She has a phone. → It is ___ phone. <strong style="color:var(--green-dark)">(her)</strong></li>
        <li>✗ This is mine book. → ✓ This is ___ book. <strong style="color:var(--green-dark)">(my)</strong></li>
        <li>✗ Is this he phone? → ✓ Is this ___ phone? <strong style="color:var(--green-dark)">(his)</strong></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 12. 자가진단 체크리스트 -->
  <div class="section" id="s11">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num" style="background:var(--brown);">12</div>
      <div><span class="section-title">자가진단 체크리스트</span><span class="section-en">SELF-CHECK</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li onclick="this.querySelector('.chk').classList.toggle('on')"><div class="chk"></div> 소유 형용사(my, your, his, her)가 무엇인지 이해했다.</li>
        <li onclick="this.querySelector('.chk').classList.toggle('on')"><div class="chk"></div> 소유 형용사를 명사 앞에 올바르게 배치할 수 있다.</li>
        <li onclick="this.querySelector('.chk').classList.toggle('on')"><div class="chk"></div> 남성(his)과 여성(her)의 소유 형태를 구분할 수 있다.</li>
        <li onclick="this.querySelector('.chk').classList.toggle('on')"><div class="chk"></div> mine/me 대신 my를 사용하는 등 흔한 실수를 교정할 수 있다.</li>
        <li onclick="this.querySelector('.chk').classList.toggle('on')"><div class="chk"></div> 질문과 대답에서 소유 형용사를 자연스럽게 사용할 수 있다.</li>
        <li onclick="this.querySelector('.chk').classList.toggle('on')"><div class="chk"></div> my와 mine의 차이를 설명할 수 있다.</li>
        <li onclick="this.querySelector('.chk').classList.toggle('on')"><div class="chk"></div> It's와 Its의 차이를 이해했다.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="footer-nav">
  <a href="G10_new.html" class="fnav-btn fnav-prev">← G10</a>
  <span class="fnav-center">G11 · POSSESSIVE FORMS</span>
  <a href="G12_new.html" class="fnav-btn fnav-next">G12 →</a>
